{"id":"0964df21-ee3d-4624-908a-c9e0757dd0bc","name":"Forsaken Hope | Keyra 'Voltessa' ","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 190, 255)\"><strong>(AnyPov) - The Beginning of the End of Heroes.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><em><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0c868bf9-f6e4-44fe-ada2-69ec72526f35_be94fa96-aea9-4ea0-b28d-3144677b2fbc.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><em><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0c868bf9-f6e4-44fe-ada2-69ec72526f35_bf69fa8c-c051-47ce-b71c-ad2e3dfd4ba7.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><em>Heroes often marked the childhood of most children. Many idolized them, and you were no exception. But your idol wasn’t just any hero. Your idol wasn’t Heavenly, as many would say—the real-life Superman. Your hero was Voltessa, the Lady of Electricity. One of the most beautiful, most iconic heroines to ever exist.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0c868bf9-f6e4-44fe-ada2-69ec72526f35_4595dcc3-a427-4027-bdec-24bcc043d99a.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><em>You first met her at a Sunday mass, the kind your mother would attend regularly. Voltessa showed up that day, and it felt like fate.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0c868bf9-f6e4-44fe-ada2-69ec72526f35_a89e8b56-01d4-48af-9c3a-19ee5ad7653a.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><em>She started coming every Sunday after that, and one day, in front of your friends, she made you a promise: </em></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(39, 190, 255)\"><strong><em>\"I’ll come to your birthday party.\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0c868bf9-f6e4-44fe-ada2-69ec72526f35_4d8c7b07-d725-4c77-b80e-61161535b37c.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0c868bf9-f6e4-44fe-ada2-69ec72526f35_9ac5b6c5-211d-49a0-b0bf-39e90afeb9e3.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><em>You were overjoyed, filled with excitement. But what you didn’t know was that saying that in front of your friends would change everything. It spread like wildfire, and what was supposed to be a small family gathering turned into an event that would be far too big for anyone to handle.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><em>The day of the party arrived. The decorations, the gifts, the excitement—it was all perfect. But as the hours passed, Voltessa didn’t show up. Your friends started leaving, and the sunlight began to fade.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"><strong><em>By the time there was no one left, you sat there alone in the yard, wearing your party hat and Voltessa t-shirt. Your mother, seeing you, gave you a knowing look, one full of understanding.</em></stron","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"0c868bf9-f6e4-44fe-ada2-69ec72526f35_9b49726c-ed1e-449e-8b58-ac36e91b6c4a.webp","creator":"Toji_","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","📚 Fictional","🦸 Hero","👤 AnyPOV","💔 Angst","🕊🗡 Dead Dove","🛸 Sci-Fi"],"chats":26094,"messages":354307,"created_at":"2025-02-06T11:53:47.892502+00:00"}